short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Find out what was used to make a website

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
MadeWith is a simple and efficient browser extension that helps you identify the technologies used to create any website you visit. Whether it's built with WordPress, Webflow, Framer, Shopify, or other popular platforms, MadeWith will give you the insights you need.

Key Features:
- Instantly detects the platform used to build a website.
- Provides detailed information about the main font used on the site.
- View all fonts used on the website with a simple click.
- Easy-to-use interface with a sleek design.
- Developed by WebBuilders for developers, designers, and curious users.

MadeWith helps you understand the web better by providing detailed information about the building blocks of your favorite websites.
